        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/rick_allen/{size}/90255_2.png",
        "created_at": "2019-01-25T18:32:57.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>John Paul\u2019s business strategy is to sell virtually all his wine to retail outlets.  He isn\u2019t interested in having a bunch of fans invading the winery - too much of an interruption to his job of growing grapes and making wine.  About the only way you get in to see him right now is if you know something about voles.  They have been attacking vines in the Clos Electrique vineyard and he\u2019s looking for solutions.  If not, come down the week before Thanksgiving and I\u2019ll introduce you.</p>",
